      "title": "语气副词「吧」— The Modal Particle ba",
      "explanation": "吧(ba) is added at the end of a sentence to soften its tone and make it less direct. 建议 Suggestion: 我们走吧! (Let's go!) — use 吧 to make a suggestion. Confirmation: 你是小明吧？ (You're Xiao Ming, right?) — use 吧 to seek agreement. 命令 Mild command: 快点儿吧! (Hurry up!) — use 吧 to soften a command.",
      "examples": [
